{"about_the_game":"It's December 2025, You play as Sarah Caldwell, an ex-military sharpshooter, in &quot;Radiant Exodus&quot; a riveting 3D FPS set against the radiant backdrop of Gleam City. A night that begins with a simple meeting at a bar spirals into chaos when a UFO descends, unleashing a horde of mutants onto the streets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/BarGif1.gif?t=1727602899\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/StreetGif5.gif?t=1727602899\" /><br>With her AK47 in hand, Sarah must fend off the mutant waves and navigate the pandemonium to uncover the truth behind this alien invasion. Each shot counts in your quest to eliminate the mutant threat and protect the city that never sleeps.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/NewGif_3.gif?t=1727602899\" /><br>Key Features:<br><br>Intense Shooter Gameplay: Experience the thrill of survival as you combat relentless mutant enemies.<br>Luminous Urban Setting: Fight through the dazzling, light-filled streets of a city under siege.<br>Progressive Challenges: Adapt to evolving objectives and uncover the secrets of the mutants' arrival.<br>&quot;Radiant Exodus&quot; is your battleground. Gear up for a fight where only the bravest stand tall. Will you rise as the light of Gleam City?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/extras/M3.gif?t=1727602899\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727602899","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/page.bg.jpg?t=1727602899","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920120/f1de45a5820aaea015f2f94668cd51198d6a5c1a